sec.p:
In-depth interviews were conducted with five specialists, one PC nurse, six LHWs, and the field study coordinator. Rating how useful or helpful mPCL was on a scale of 1 to 10, scores ranged from 7 to 10 with a mean score of 9.1 (SD = 1.12); participants were generally likely to recommend mPCL to a colleague (NPS = 92; mean score of 9.6 out of 10, SD = 0.87, range = 7,10) (
Table 1
).
